<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.8">
<l>attā variyē yeṉṟuṉṉaiya ḻaikka</l>
<l>pittā veṉṟupē cukiṉṟārpiṟa reṉṉai</l>
<l>muttē maṇimā ṇikkamēmuḷaik kiṉṟa</l>
<l>vittē yuṉṉaiyeṅ ṅaṉamnāṉviṭu kēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I call out to you, saying “Father, lion,”</l>
<l>Others say to me, ‘O mad man!’;</l>
<l>Pearl, ruby jewel, ripening seed,</l>
<l>How [would] I leave you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
